claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics1, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics2, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics3, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics4, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics5, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics6, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics7, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics8, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics9, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics10, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics11, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics12, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics13, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics14, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics15, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics16, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics17, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics18, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics19, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics20, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics21, claim.UWAlrtHazardCharacteristics22, claim.EBEmailClaimInd, claim.LinkCompanion, claim.LinkCompanionDate, claim.NamedStormInd, claim.FloodInsuranceInd, claim.FloodInsuranceCompany, claim.FloodInsurancePolicy, claim.FloodInsPolEffDate, claim.FloodInsPolExpDate, claim.ReportedToProducerBy, claim.ReceivedBy, claim.OtherDesc, claim.NoPaymentReason, claim.OtherNoPaymentReason, claim.LossNoticeNumber, claim.RowId ,
claimPolicyInfo.policynumber,
case when length(claimPolicyInfo.policyversion)='1' then concat('00',claimPolicyInfo.policyversion)
when length(claimPolicyInfo.policyversion)='2' then concat('0',claimPolicyInfo.policyversion)
else claimPolicyInfo.policyversion end as policyversion, case when claim.typecd='Claim' then PolicyRisk.RiskIdRef else null end as PolicyRiskIdref, UnderlyingPersonalLiability FROM
 claim left join (Select PolicyNumber,PolicyVersion, SystemId, UnderlyingPersonalLiability from claimPolicyInfo where  ClaimPolicyinfo.cmmcontainer='Claim') ClaimPolicyInfo on 
Claim.Systemid=ClaimPolicyinfo.Systemid 
Left join (select systemid,id, riskidref from PolicyRisk) PolicyRisk on claim.riskidref = PolicyRisk.id 
where 
claim.cmmcontainer='Claim' and claim.systemid in (select systemid from advrxxchangedbeans where 
-- concat(adddt,addtm)>='$$m_strtdt' and 
-- concat(adddt,addtm) <='$$m_Enddt' and
 cmmcontainer='Claim') limit 500;
